   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Who is this Leon?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>So Ghoul Baldness was… Ah… How did it become like this…<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jermain sobs)</FONT><BR>
my master must still be waiting for Leon. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Listen to the story)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Leon</FONT>… <BR>It will be a long story. I will tell you the story if you are not in a rush.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What happened? Did something bad happen?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>10 years ago, <FONT color=#a82424>a brilliant shining star</FONT> appeared at the north of the continent.<BR>
That was the star that was foretold in the <FONT color=#a82424>Sage's Prophecy</FONT>.<BR>
Everyone thought it was a good omen. However, that was not the case in reality.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask about the Black Monster)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>
Yes. Right after the star had appeared, monsters started to become more active in the north of the continent.<BR>
And among them was a bizarre-looking <FONT color=#a82424>Black Monster</FONT> which was never seen before.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" image="QW_CataractGateway.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The Order deployed clerics to various parts of the continent to investigate on the Black Monster. According to their reports, the monsters' movements started from the north and they were travelling down towards the south. And they found out that their destination was none other than <FONT color=#a82424>Calderock Village</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask about the family)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>So my master and I were deployed here to investigate on the mastermind behind the monsters. And we found out a shocking fact. <FONT color=#a82424>The black monsters were after a family</FONT> .</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why were they being pursued?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The family consisted of a man named <FONT color=#a82424>Leon</FONT>, his wife <FONT color=#a82424>Clara</FONT>, and their <FONT color=#a82424>young daughter</FONT>. At first, we were suspicious if they were being chased because they aroused the monsters. But they were just simply being chased for no clear reason.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" mid="62" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He must have been a brave man.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I don't know. <FONT color=#a82424>my master seemed to have noticed something</FONT>, but he didn't mention anything in particular. However, ever since they arrived in this village, a fierce fight with the monsters took place. Leon took charge to lead in the battle.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-i" mid="64" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Yes, a brave man he was. There were many people who blamed him for bringing the monsters to this village at first, but they all became moved by his attitude in the end.<BR>Everyone fought bravely against the monsters, but it was not an easy fight.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-i" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" mid="66" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> It sounds like the Forest of Death. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Elf in red</FONT> was cunning, and the <FONT color=#a82424>poison from dead monsters' bodies</FONT> was lethal. There were no living things found near where the monsters died for a long time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" image="QW_17.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-k" mid="68" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>You're clever. <FONT color=#a82424>Forest of Death was a place that was used to lure the monsters to kill all of them at once</FONT>. It was probably the best option they had to minimize the area of contamination.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-l" mid="70" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>During the process of luring monster many were sacrificed. <BR>Despite the sacrifices, the monsters gained an upper hand in the battle. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-m" mid="72" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How did things go for him?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>After safely evacuating his wife and his daughter, he left a few words with my master and gave him his <FONT color=#a82424>pendant</FONT>.<BR>Then he headed towards the Sleepers' Temple all by himself.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-m" image="QW_16.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-n" mid="74" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything I can do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Nobody knows what happened to him. Something must have happened at the <FONT color=#a82424>Sleepers' Temple</FONT>…. I retreated following my master's orders, but he stayed back till the end. He must have waited for Leon until the moment he passed away.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-n" image="QW_16.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" mid="78" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll investigate the Sleepers' Temple. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I'm sorry to trouble you… Please go to the <FONT color=#a82424>Sleepers' Temple</FONT> and find out how Leon died. I hope my master can rest in peace if he hears about his last moments.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300014" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Sleepers' Temple</FONT> was the last place where Leon went to.<BR>Please investigate the area and find any of his remains.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3-a" mid="87" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Explain what happened at the Sleepers' Temple)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Did you manage to find anything related to Leon?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
